    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Begin a thrilling journey through time with Nia, a brave young girl who finds herself transported to an ancient world filled with mysteries and dangers.</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/1eb14374f375b1532cac373c48060dc7.avif?t=1759685051\" width=768 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this captivating platformer, you’ll venture into a past where myths and legends intertwine, guiding Nia on her quest to return home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in this hostile world, Nia must navigate her way back by overcoming numerous trials, solving ancient puzzles, and dodging dangers at every turn. Explore mysterious ruins, uncover hidden artifacts, and tackle intricate mechanisms that can either be your salvation or doom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect ancient artifacts, activate portals, and find the exit on each level to help Nia return to the modern world. Your wit, agility, and keen observation will be the keys to success in this remarkable adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/7eed1130eeffb3ebceec016f40fdd32d.poster.avif?t=1759685051\" width=760 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/7eed1130eeffb3ebceec016f40fdd32d.webm?t=1759685051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/7eed1130eeffb3ebceec016f40fdd32d.mp4?t=1759685051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric World</strong>: Explore a setting inspired by the ancient civilizations of Egypt and Greece. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Puzzles</strong>: Solve challenges rooted in myths and legends. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exciting Levels</strong>: Conquer unique obstacles and trials. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vibrant Graphics and Enchanting Music</strong>: Immerse yourself in the ancient world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intriguing Story</strong>: Experience a narrative full of unexpected twists and secrets. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/2b372d52e28e659b49e0de0507a347ce.poster.avif?t=1759685051\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/2b372d52e28e659b49e0de0507a347ce.webm?t=1759685051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033710/extras/2b372d52e28e659b49e0de0507a347ce.mp4?t=1759685051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Nia and uncover the secrets of ancient civilizations!</p>",
